entries.title_d: You must deliver the encrypted documents to a RSF contact in the Lok System.
entries.title: Lok System: Deliver Encrypted Documents to the RSF Contact
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 I hate to throw you to the Swamp Stalkers here Captain but we are about to do just that.  There is a vulnerability in the Black Sun communications net we want to exploit but it is in Black Sun controlled area.  You will be a major target. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Meet up with a RSF Rawl here
entries.quest_location_d: An area of  Black Sun activity
entries.quest_dock2_d: Use the /dock command to transfer your cargo
entries.hello_d: This is Captain Dekert, Command said to expect you.
entries.found_loc_d: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 We are uploading some coordinates to you now.  We have a rawl out there to meet you.  We have more tasks when it is finished. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.docking_complete_delivery: The dock looks good, send over the cargo.
entries.attack_stopped: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Hostile Activity has ceased. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Enemy craft detected on attack vector. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrived_at_delivery: \#pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Designated rendezvous point reached. \#pcontrast3 >
